local Manager = s_WordDictionaryDatabase; Manager.allwords["endothermic"]={"endothermic","[,endəʊ'θɜːmɪk]","[,ɛndo'θɝmɪk]","adj.吸热的",'adj.吸热的(吸热反应的,内热的)','Animals, like humans, that control their body temperature internally are called “endothermic.” Endotherms generate heat internally by increasing the rate at which they metabolize fats and sugars.','像人类一样通过内部调节体温的动物则被称作“恒温动物”。恒温动物是通过加快它们脂肪和糖类的新陈代谢使体内产生热量的。','At very high temperatures, more endothermic reactions play a role.','在很高的温度下，更多的吸热反应起作用。'}
